Package org.gvsig.educa.portableview.app.editor

PortableView gvSIG's editor plugin Allows PortableView creation and editing into gvSIG.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CompilationListener
    Portable View Document compilation listener
    PortableViewEditorManager
    Manager which make easy the creation, editing and share PortableView This uses all services of PortableViewManager and PortableViewSwingManager in a high level way.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExportPortableViewToViewExtension
    Andami extension to create a View from a Portable view data.
    GeneratePackagePortableViewExtension
    Andami extension to create a gvSIG package of a Portable View.
    NewPortableViewExtension
    Andami extension to create a Portable view from a View.
    OpenRelatedDocumentExtension
    Abstract Andami extension which opens a the related document: source view of a portable view or related portable view of a view
    OpenRelatedPortableViewExtension
    Andami extension which opens related portable view of a view
    OpenSourceViewExtension
    Andami extension which opens source view of a portable view
    PortableViewEditorExtension
    Andami extension which initializes the document actions related to PortableView creation, editing and share.
    PortableViewEditorLibrary
    Library for API of services to create, export and update PortableView documents.
    PortableViewEditorLocator
    Locator which provide access to the services to create, modify and share PortableView
    RegeneratePortableViewExtension
    Andami extension to update a Portable View from its source View.
